For running on linux-

Ensure "attr" package is installed.

Additionally, the
extended attributes need to be in "user." name space. Any attribute such as
"xyz" would fail with "operation not permitted" error. It would need to be
"user.xyz".

To set exit attribute in IOF prototype- use

setfattr -n user.exit -v 1 child_fs/Rank0


For OSX-

To run on OSX and set exit attribute for IOF prototype-

xattr -w user.exit 1 child_fs/Rank0

